{"tid":161664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天網恢恢】殺人犯潛逃17年變富翁 茶樓收租突被捕","createTime":"2017-03-18T16:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T02:59:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f60672204a1e32d7a1e1b6bfd19b39cf47de4ea","tid":161664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170318/large/1489842171_9178.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170318%2Flarge%2F1489842171_9178.jpg&h=7f035748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56446458&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56446458%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170319&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ef7be00c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56446458%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170319&h=0b1921e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56446458&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170319</a><br />\n湖南岳陽一名男子17年前因爛賭搶劫殺死一名的士司機，之後隱姓埋名，開始漫長的逃亡生涯，卻輾轉成為一名千萬富翁。日前，警方在廣州一處鬧市區的茶樓拘捕他時，這名男子還在收租。<br />\n<br />\n「我終於可以沉下心來反思了，我對不起受害人！」涉案男子李美建，中專畢業後，便直接進入雲溪鄉政府當基層公務員。但他卻沉迷賭博，結果欠下2萬多元（人民幣‧下同）的債。由於別人舉報，他被停薪留職，一時糊塗下，約下兩名友人，策劃殺人劫車，以還賭債。<br />\n<br />\n2000年11月7日下午，李美建和同夥劉黎明（化名）以租車去湖北石首市守孝為名，騙得雲溪區一名司機送他們去石首，但找不到機會落手。翌日上午，他與劉黎明又到岳陽市區，並打電話邀來另一名朋友陳勇（化名），以同樣手段騙得雲溪區司機沈X前往石首。途中，3人襲擊司機，並把他推入長江。劉黎明及陳勇先後被警方拘捕及自首，唯獨李美建如人間蒸發般，杳無信息。<br />\n<br />\n直至去年，警方發現李美建的家人似乎跟一個叫「李美才」的廣州人聯繫密切，於是再次啟動調查，發現李美才就是李美建，而且已成為廣東一名富商，經營服裝生意，資產千萬。本月8日，警員衝進廣州南沙區一家茶樓，將正在收租的李美建拘捕。李美建說：「17年了，最終還是沒能逃掉，終於還是回家了！這麼多年，我沒見過父母，沒回過家，連家鄉話都不會說了。」<br />\n<br />\n李美建供稱，當年犯案後，他斷絕與家人的所有聯繫，躲到雲南昆明，隨後偷渡出境俄羅斯。2003年，他又潛回上海，在一家企業做起管理。經過一番努力，他完成中南大學工商管理和建築專業的所有課程，還得到上海企業老闆的賞識。期間，他認識了一名溫州女孩，為了不暴露身份，決定與女友到廣東做起服裝生意。隨後生意越做越大，還有了一個美滿的家庭，育有兩女一子。可是天網恢恢，他還是被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n岳陽網"},{"pid":"9c2f0b50d7ef8d1bc3c4d168d4793edf1c56c3e9","tid":161664,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:52:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8b2bc0b8c2c6dd43c7c99ce1a095c11f85dfba4","tid":161664,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:56:24.000Z","msg":"善惡到頭終有報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c37fab53cc756842f827949285dda5326a18c9e","tid":161664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T18:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375d26330dfd5804a9c3318fd97bbe06b23bf34d","tid":161664,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改名改得你咁撚懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22926fa3baea985d8e6636dcaad60393b0ce4ce","tid":161664,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>改名改得你咁撚懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實佢唔同家人聯絡咩事都沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cd2418ea4457dbd25dfd73df9c7fe884ff4861","tid":161664,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>改名改得你咁撚懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心on 9<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor